<cubx-maps cubx-webpackage-id="cubx-maps@1.0.0-SNAPSHOT" style="height: 300px">
    <cubx-core-init style="display: none">
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="mapInitOptions">{"center": [51.505, -0.09], "zoom": 13}</cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="tileLayer">
            {
                "url": "https://a.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png",
                "leafLetOptions": {
                    "attribution": "Map data © <a href=\"https://www.openstreetmap.org/\">OpenStreetMap</a> contributors, <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/\">CC-BY-SA</a>",
                    "maxZoom": 18
                }
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="markers">{
                "list": [
                    {"latlng": [51.5, -0.09], "popUpInnerHtml": "<b>Fixed</b> Marker", "leafLetOptions": {"title": "Fixed Marker"}},
                    {"latlng": [51.51, -0.091], "leafLetOptions": {"title": "Draggable Marker", "draggable": true}}
                ]
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="circles">{
                "list": [
                    {"latlng": [51.508, -0.11], "popUpInnerHtml": "Red <b>circle</b>", "leafLetOptions": { "color": "red", "fillColor": "#f03", "fillOpacity": 0.5, "radius": 500 }}
                ]
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="polygons">{
                "list": [
                    {"latlngs": [ [51.509, -0.08], [51.503, -0.06], [51.51, -0.047] ], "popUpInnerHtml": "A <b>polygon</b>"}
                ]
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="polylines">{
                "list": [
                    {"latlngs": [ [51.5, -0.09], [51.51, -0.091] ], "popUpInnerHtml": "A <b>polyline</b>"}
                ]
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
        <cubx-core-slot-init slot="rectangles">{
                "list": [
                    {"bounds": [ [51.505, -0.13], [51.498, -0.14] ], "popUpInnerHtml": "A <b>rectangle</b>", "leafLetOptions": { "color": "#ff7800", "weight": 1 }}
                ]
            }
        </cubx-core-slot-init>
    </cubx-core-init>
</cubx-maps>
